txt.en: 'From Frodo and Sam's accounts, Torech Ungol should be empty. They found no living beings inside save Ungwet√°ri herself. That is no longer the case, as she has recalled all of her children from the wider world. I do not know if she has done this for sustenance, protection, or loneliness. I cannot pretend to fathom the mind of such an ancient and evil being as she. It matters not, the spiders are a threat and must be thinned before we enter deeper into the tunnels.'
Shelob's lair has become infested with her spider children. Legolas has asked you to thin their numbers.
'You have done well, [placeholder]. Atli will be happy to hear there are fewer spiders in the world. Alas, there will be many more to slay in our near future. The horde is nigh unending.'
The spider-horde has completely overrun Torech Ungol.\n\nYou should defeat spiders in Torech Ungol.
Legolas is standing by outside Torech Ungol.\n\nYou should talk to Legolas.
